  <h3>TableHeader</h3>
  <p>Wraps <code class="inline-code">&lt;thead&gt;</code> for column headers.</p>

  <h3>TableBody</h3>
  <p>Wraps <code class="inline-code">&lt;tbody&gt;</code> for data rows.</p>

  <h3>TableFoot</h3>
  <p>Wraps <code class="inline-code">&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> for totals/summaries.</p>

  <h3>TableRow</h3>
  <p>Wraps <code class="inline-code">&lt;tr&gt;</code> for each row.</p>

  <h3>TableHead</h3>
  <p>Wraps <code class="inline-code">&lt;th&gt;</code> for header cells.</p>

  <h3>TableCell</h3>
  <p>Wraps <code class="inline-code">&lt;td&gt;</code> for data cells.</p>
  <p><strong>Specific props:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li><code class="inline-code">colspan</code>: Number of columns to span</li>
    <li><code class="inline-code">rowspan</code>: Number of rows to span</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>TableCaption</h3>
  <p>Wraps <code class="inline-code">&lt;caption&gt;</code> for the table description.</p>

  <h2 id="accessibility">Accessibility</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>HTML semantics:</strong> Uses native <code class="inline-code">&lt;table&gt;</code>, <code class="inline-code">&lt;thead&gt;</code>, <code class="inline-code">&lt;tbody&gt;</code>, <code class="inline-code">&lt;th&gt;</code>, <code class="inline-code">&lt;td&gt;</code> tags</li>
    <li><strong>Caption:</strong> Always add a <code class="inline-code">TableCaption</code> to describe the table</li>
    <li><strong>Scope:</strong> <code class="inline-code">&lt;th&gt;</code> cells automatically have <code class="inline-code">scope=\"col\"</code></li>
    <li><strong>Responsive:</strong> Horizontal scroll preserved with keyboard focus</li>
    <li><strong>Contrast:</strong> Colors meet WCAG AA requirements</li>
    <li><strong>Hover:</strong> Clear hover states for navigation</li>
  </ul>

