  <h2>Best practices</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Caption required:</strong> Always add a <code class="inline-code">TableCaption</code> for accessibility</li>
    <li><strong>Clear headers:</strong> Use descriptive labels in <code class="inline-code">TableHead</code></li>
    <li><strong>Consistent data:</strong> Align data types (numbers right, text left)</li>
    <li><strong>Striped for lists:</strong> Use <code class="inline-code">striped</code> for tables with many rows</li>
    <li><strong>Limit columns:</strong> Maximum 8-10 columns for readability</li>
    <li><strong>Responsive:</strong> Test on mobile - horizontal scroll must work</li>
    <li><strong>Inline actions:</strong> Place action buttons in the last column</li>
    <li><strong>Footer for totals:</strong> Use <code class="inline-code">TableFoot</code> for summaries</li>
  </ul>
